{"tid":1396372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump 出招加關稅！香港人罷工好有用架！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T05:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:31:19.000Z","uid":296510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3662670a13b9887909ec3bccea3a052859040ce4","tid":1396372,"uid":296510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"唔好再話罷工有咩用，依家Trump出招，將對餘下總值3千億美元的中國貨品，九月一日起徵收百之十關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>即係點？香港要助攻！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n//8月5日罷工有用架，8月5日如果貨櫃碼頭罷工，貨櫃碼頭射波射足一個禮拜，原定8月5日離港嘅貨船搞到8月12日至離開，根據東方海外船期表，會搞到批貨趕唔切9月1日抵達美國長島，屆時我食花生成批貨硬食百分之十關稅，而且如果由周末起計，到下個禮拜，香港港口運作大亂，好多船去唔到鹽田式蛇口接貨，或者嚟香港轉口啲貨無法準時到港口，我真係睇成棚貨九月一日至到美國港口係乜嘢花生境況。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcegzLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcegzLM.jpg&h=297fe311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載文章：Trump 突然出招玩殘中國 --- 黃世澤<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/28170/trump-%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%9B%E7%8E%A9%E6%AE%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F28170%2Ftrump-%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2584%25B6%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%258B%259B%25E7%258E%25A9%25E6%25AE%2598%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=16790a59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/28170/trump-%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%9B%E7%8E%A9%E6%AE%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a>"}]}